txt.en: You are a ranger, dispatched to keep safe the contested borderlands of the Ettenmoors from the Witch-king's army. In your many years, you have become skilled with both the bow and the blade. In addition, you know how to move across the land in silence and unseen, allowing you to take your foes by surprise.
